inish">减</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-4" title="List of HSK 4 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 4 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 844</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 1078</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/一味" title="yi1 wei4">一味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/串味" title="chuan4 wei4">串味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/乏味" title="fa2 wei4">乏味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/五味" title="wu3 wei4">五味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/京味" title="jing1 wei4">京味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/入味" title="ru4 wei4">入味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/口味" title="kou3 wei4">口味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/吃味" title="chi1 wei4">吃味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/味儿" title="wei4 r5">味儿</a>, <a href="/dictionary/味噌" title="wei4 ceng1">味噌</a>, <a href="/dictionary/味精" title="wei4 jing1">味精</a>, <a href="/dictionary/味素" title="wei4 su4">味素</a>, <a href="/dictionary/味蕾" title="wei4 lei3">味蕾</a>, <a href="/dictionary/味觉" title="wei4 jue2">味觉</a>, <a href="/dictionary/味道" title="wei4 dao5">味道</a>, <a href="/dictionary/品味" title="pin3 wei4">品味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/回味" title="hui2 wei4">回味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/够味" title="gou4 wei4">够味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/寻味" title="xun2 wei4">寻味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/后味" title="hou4 wei4">后味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/怪味" title="guai4 wei4">怪味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/情味" title="qing2 wei4">情味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/意味" title="yi4 wei4">意味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/提味" title="ti2 wei4">提味</a>, <a href="/dictionary/有味" title="you3 wei4">有味</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">味[<span style="color:#000099;">wèi</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- taste<br>- smell<br>- classifier for drugs (in TCM)<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><